<i>Bunker, yeah.</i>

15:45.076 --> 15:47.377
<i>Well, your neighbor</i>
<i>Mr. mcnab--</i>
<i>mcnab?</i>

15:47.445 --> 15:51.749
Yeah. Mcnab called to tell you
that two jigaboos just robbed...

15:51.816 --> 15:55.619
Morgan's jewelry store
and they hidin'
in the neighborhood.

15:55.687 --> 15:57.621
Hi. How are ya?

15:59.457 --> 16:02.159
And in the house
that they's hidin' in...

16:02.226 --> 16:04.762
They just picked up
a few odds and ends...

16:04.829 --> 16:06.931
Just to keep
from being shiftless.

16:08.232 --> 16:11.068
- You got any questions?
- No, I got no questions.

16:11.135 --> 16:14.371
I got a question.
Will you
stifle yourself!

16:14.439 --> 16:18.876
I was wondering what happened
to my husband's killer dog.

16:19.945 --> 16:22.746
Oh, the dog.

16:22.814 --> 16:26.450
You know, I'm afraid we had
to put the dog to sleep.

16:26.517 --> 16:28.686
You ain't mad at us?

16:28.753 --> 16:30.955
